For Training
https://excalidraw.com/

- npm install prisma --save-dev Or npm i -D prisma
- npx prisma init

Note: Anytime you change your model make sure you run migrate:

- npx prisma migrate dev --name init

Install prisma client

- npm install @prisma/client

Whenever you update your Prisma schema you will have to update your database schema using either

- 'prisma migrate dev' or 'prisma db push'
- npx prisma studio

Install bctypt to encrypt password

- npm i bcrypt
- npm i axios

https://next-auth.js.org
Install Next-Auth

- npm install next-auth

You need to install prisma Adapter
https://www.npmjs.com/package/@next-auth/prisma-adapter

- npm i @next-auth/prisma-adapter

Dependency to Install

- npm i react-icons zod use-debounce clsx axios
- npm i use-debounce
- npm i react-toastify OR npm i sonner
